								<article class="entry post-27261 post type-post status-publish hentry tag-democratic-party tag-great-depression-1930s tag-presidential-election-of-2016 tag-roosevelt-franklin-delano tag-sanders-bernard tag-socialism-theory-and-philosophy per-roosevelt-franklin-delano per-sanders-bernard des-great-depression-1930s des-presidential-election-of-2016 des-socialism-theory-and-philosophy org-democratic-party" id="post-27261">
